flowchart LR
    RiskKafka[(Kafka Topic: risk.evaluated.v1)] --> Consumer[Risk Evaluated Event Consumer]

    Consumer --> AlertCreationService[Alert Creation Service]
    AlertCreationService --> PriorityMapper[Alert Priority Mapper]
    AlertCreationService --> AlertRepository[Alert Repository]

    AlertRepository --> AlertsDB[(Alerts Table)]

    Client[Client / Future UI] --> AlertAPI[Alert REST API]
    AlertAPI --> QueryService[Alert Query Service]
    QueryService --> AlertsDB

    AlertAPI --> StatusUpdateService[Alert Status Update Service]
    StatusUpdateService --> AlertRepository

    StatusUpdateService --> Assignment[Assigned Analyst]
    StatusUpdateService --> Status[Alert Status]

    AlertsDB --> Filters[Status / Priority / Risk Filters]
    Filters --> AlertAPI
